Early Autumn

Beneath a sky of sapphire blue,  
light clouds drift softly through,  
whispering tales of warm, gentle days,  
as the mild wind gently sways.

Leaves begin their quiet turn—  
a hint of yellow in each burnished fern,  
while the grass still holds its emerald hue,  
in the quiet neighborhood, I walk anew.

The sun warms my face, tender and bright,  
while shadows stretch in soft delight,  
a season’s whisper, calm and clear,  
early autumn’s beauty, serenely near.

初秋

宝蓝色的天空下，
轻盈的云朵轻柔地飘过，
低声诉说着温暖柔和的日子，
和煦的微风轻轻摇曳。

树叶开始静静地变色——
每一株光亮的蕨类植物都泛着淡淡的黄色，
而小草依然保持着翠绿色，
在宁静的街区，我重新开始行走。

阳光温暖地照耀着我的脸庞，温柔而明亮，
阴影在柔和的喜悦中延伸，
季节的低语，平静而清晰，
初秋的美景，静谧而近在咫尺。
